    protected static class SimplexTable.SimpleTableIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<Simplex>
    Instances provide Iterator for non-destructive iterating over entries. That is, repeated iteration over an SimplexTable instance is possible with multiple instances of this class.
